# Input

```html
@if (user.isHuman) {
<human-profile [data]="user" />
} @else if (user.isRobot) {
<!-- robot users are rare, so load their profiles lazily -->
@defer {
<robot-profile [data]="user" />
}
} @else {
<p>The profile is unknown!</p>
}

```


